{"tid":2275508,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"實測sony黑科技！玩手機game唔熱、唔損耗電池！","createTime":"2020-11-07T08:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T05:42:33.000Z","uid":109923,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"41358d20e3a329ed93f8a7e3a1bbd13ba625b9da","tid":2275508,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T08:06:59.000Z","msg":"前情提要：<br />\nsony智能電話電源管理再次領先全球！叉電打機時，唔消耗電池！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2094918\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2094918</a><br />\n<br />\n實測：<br />\n<br />\nSony Xperia 加入了 H.S. 電源控制功能，當用家在接駁電源線打機時，它會暫停以手機內置電池供電，而是直接用外置電源供電，避免在充電的時候，同時使用內置電池。一來這可以有效延長電池壽命，二來可以避免充電的時候同時使用手機出現的機身發熱情況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jp3co4F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjp3co4F.jpg&h=a7e28c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲在遊戲增強器中，Sony 在 Xperia 5 II 中加入了「H.S. 電源控制」這個新功能。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eFb9rh3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeFb9rh3.jpg&h=c9a3be63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲當用家想在接駁火牛後長時間玩遊戲時開啟了此功能，它就只會透過火牛為手機提供電源，既不會同時為手機內鋰電池充電，亦不會用到鋰電池的電量。當停止玩遊戲時，或者拔除 USB 線，才會重新為手機充電或使用內置鋰電池為手機提供電量。這樣就可以確保電池壽命不會耗用得太快。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E3tLJ4N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE3tLJ4N.jpg&h=175b4b6e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n▲此功能的另一個優點，就是不會令手機出現辣手情況。但究竟是否屬實？筆者就以測溫槍測試了一下，首先在未玩遊戲兼未接駁火牛提供電源時，Xperia 5 II 的機背溫度大約是 27.5 度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZjcTSX8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZjcTSX8.jpg&h=ce049f15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲當接駁了火牛為手機充電時，機背溫度就提升至 29.4 度，這個提升幅度亦是十分正常。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KMo4fbs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKMo4fbs.jpg&h=ef580990&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲當在接駁著火牛提供電源情況下玩了半小時遊戲後，筆者再以測溫槍量度 Xperia 5 II 機背溫度，也只是輕微提升了不足 4 度至 33 度左右，由此可見 Sony 新加入的 H.S. 電源控制功能確實能發揮效用。<br />\n<br />\n汁：<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/11/04/sony-xperia-5-ii-gaming-experience-review/mobile-phone/?fbclid=IwAR0PKpckFcEH3kFaodeC6JaCdWuwSD7cJ2JuVOze5URGQXOWBhIbgVrssn4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F11%2F04%2Fsony-xperia-5-ii-gaming-experience-review%2Fmobile-phone%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0PKpckFcEH3kFaodeC6JaCdWuwSD7cJ2JuVOze5URGQXOWBhIbgVrssn4&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuKxOsK%2BJamotDVaNSe1I1zI%3D&h=877acec7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/11/04/sony-xperia-5-ii-gaming-experience-review/mobile-phone/?fbclid=IwAR0PKpckFcEH3kFaodeC6JaCdWuwSD7cJ2JuVOze5URGQXOWBhIbgVrssn4</a>"},{"pid":"66641be40969f320891091544d7419290d8e467d","tid":2275508,"uid":109923,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T08:08:39.000Z","msg":"麻煩其他廠生性小小，快啲抄呢個功能啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7474fcc82ce473ab50b79490797b14f04628553c","tid":2275508,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T08:09:06.000Z","msg":"都唔係好高科技啫，<br />\n手提電腦都有啦"},{"pid":"d39fd4d729743c91c38552e577d4709ff48f9da3","tid":2275508,"uid":109923,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"7474fcc82ce473ab50b79490797b14f04628553c","tid":2275508,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T08:09:06.000Z","msg":"都唔係好高科技啫，<br />\n手提電腦都有啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T08:09:59.000Z","msg":"咪就係laptop有，偏偏手機冇"},{"pid":"bf57233daf75d4848db000668d7dbbbafe7291ef","tid":2275508,"uid":164092,"like":3,"dislike":24,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T08:13:50.000Z","msg":"打機邊嗰想連住線打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327affa751089f1224814f7b13276663f30aa5d0","tid":2275508,"uid":70488,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T08:19:59.000Z","msg":"食屎啦索尼"},{"pid":"4be4f60374f7e1a